      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FRED THE FOX (1) was a little disappointing last start at Bendigo when 5th (24.27) over 425m. Strike rate this course and distance strong having won two of two tries. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to his name from five starts. Has ability and can bounce back. BUSH PROFIT (6) was below best last time finishing eighth at Healesville, but prior to that had been racing well including a Grade 5 win two back at Geelong. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. BLACK STATESMAN (5) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing sixth (23.90) in a Grade 5 at Horsham. Form here sound including two wins. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Leading chance. ASTON TELMONT (2) should be thereabouts despite an unplaced run here most recently.",
